tes-available-now/|archive-date=2018-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT202092|title=關於 iOS 4.0.2 Update for iPhone and iPod touch 的安全性內容|newspaper=Apple Support|accessdate=2018-07-24|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180722125251/https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT202092|archive-date=2018-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此更新也修補了越獄工具[[JailbreakMe|JailbreakMe]]使用的[[Safari|Safari]]漏洞<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://osxdaily.com/2010/08/11/ios-4-0-2-update-available-download/|title=iOS 4.0.2 update available to download for iPhone & iPod touch|date=2010-08-12|newspaper=OS X Daily|accessdate=2018-07-24|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180724183638/http://osxdaily.com/2010/08/11/ios-4-0-2-update-available-download/|archive-date=2018-07-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年9月8日，iOS4.1發布。此更新為[[iPhone_4|iPhone 4]]加入了[[高動態範圍成像|HDR]]功能、{{link-en|高畫質影片|High-definition video|HD影片}}上傳功能及線上租借電視影集功能，並新增社群服務[[Game_Center|Game Center]]及[[iTunes_Ping|iTunes Ping]]<ref name=":2">{{Cite news|url=https://www.imore.com/ios-4-1-review|title=iOS 4.1 review|newspaper=iMore|accessdate=2018-07-24|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170520222218/http://www.imore.com/ios-4-1-review|archive-date=2017-05-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":16">{{Cite news|url=https://mashable.com/2010/09/01/ios-4-1/#rQO.rfQpSsqI|title=iOS 4.1 and iOS 4.2 on the Way: HDR, Game Center and iPad Support|last=Warren|first=Christina|newspaper=Mashable|accessdate=2018-07-24|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615051115/https://mashable.com/2010/09/01/ios-4-1/#rQO.rfQpSsqI|archive-date=2018-06-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="appleDEV2">{{cite web|url=https://developer.apple.com/technologies/iphone/whats-new.html#gamecenter|title=What's New in iOS 4|accessdate=2010-06-14|publisher=Apple Inc.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100617053052/http://developer.apple.com/technologies/iphone/whats-new.html#gamecenter|archive-date=2010-06-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此更新也解決了內建感應器故障、[[藍牙|藍牙]]收訊不良及[[iPhone_3G|iPhone 3G]]效能下降及電池壽命縮減的問題，並修補了[[FaceTime|FaceTime]]通訊漏洞及[[WebKit|WebKit]]漏洞<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT202111|title=關於適用於 iPhone 和 iPod touch 的 iOS 4.1 之安全性內容|newspaper=Apple Support|accessdate=2018-07-24|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180722113628/https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT202111|archive-date=2018-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":21">{{cite web|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2010/09/08/apple-releases-ios-4-1-for-iphone-and-ipod-touch/|title=Apple Releases iOS 4.1 for iPhone and iPod Touch|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-09-08|last=Slivka|first=Eric|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180511012651/https://www.macrumors.com/2010/09/08/apple-releases-ios-4-1-for-iphone-and-ipod-touch/|archive-date=2018-05-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

