ve-date=2017-04-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，為所有版本的iPhone 4引進Wi-Fi熱點功能<ref name=":7" /><ref name=":8" /><ref name=":9" />，並新增[[iTunes|iTunes]]家庭共享功能<ref name=":7" /><ref name=":8" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2011/03/04/ios-4-3-brings-a-handful-of-new-features-and-new-headaches/|title=iOS 4.3 brings a handful of new features and new headaches|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2011-03-04|last=Rawson|first=Chris|publisher=[[AOL|AOL]]|website=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510104259/https://www.engadget.com/2011/03/04/ios-4-3-brings-a-handful-of-new-features-and-new-headaches/|archive-date=2017-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此后，iOS 4.3.1、iOS 4.3.2、iOS 4.3.3、iOS 4.3.4陆续发布。4.3.1更新解決了iPod touch螢幕故障及連接電視時螢幕閃爍的問題<ref name=":10">{{cite web|url=https://arstechnica.com/apple/2011/03/ios-431-fixes-ipod-touch-graphics-glitch-tv-flickering-issue/|title=iOS 4.3.1 fixes iPod touch graphics glitch, TV flickering issue|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2011-03-25|last=Cheng|first=Jacqui|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170511075338/https://arstechnica.com/apple/2011/03/ios-431-fixes-ipod-touch-graphics-glitch-tv-flickering-issue/|archive-date=2017-05-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":11">{{Cite news|url=http://osxdaily.com/2011/03/25/ios-4-3-1-download/|title=iOS 4.3.1 Download is Available Now|date=2011-03-25|newspaper=OS X Daily|accessdate=2018-07-24|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615150736/http://osxdaily.com/2011/03/25/ios-4-3-1-download/|archive-date=2018-06-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並進一步提高了iPhone系列的收訊穩定度<ref name=":10" /><ref name=":11" />。4.3.2更新解決了[[FaceTime|FaceTime]]影像延遲問題<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://osxdaily.com/2011/04/14/ios-4-3-2-download/|title=iOS 4.3.2 Download is Available Now|date=2011-04-14|newspaper=OS X Daily|accessdate=2018-07-24|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615150750/http://osxdaily.com/2011/04/14/ios-4-3-2-download/|archive-date=2018-06-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並修正了[[iPad|iPad]]系列的收訊問題<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1159239/ios432.html|title=Apple releases iOS 4.3.2, fixes FaceTime, 3G issues|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2011-04-14|last=Friedman|first=Lex|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510170134/http://www.macworld.com/article/1159239/ios432.html|archive-date=2017-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4.3.3修補了[[定常系統|定位系統]]不準確的問題<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://support.apple.com/kb/DL1358?locale=zh_TW&viewlocale=zh_TW|title=iOS 4.3.3 軟體更新|accessdate=2018-07-24|work=support.apple.com|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110415124119/http://support.apple.com/kb/DL1358?viewlocale=zh_TW&locale=zh_TW|archive-date=2011-04-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1159643/ios433_location_fixes.html|title=Apple releases iOS 4.3.3 to patch location bugs|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2011-05-04|last=Moren|first=Dan|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619040516/http://www.macworld.com/article/1159643/ios433_location_fixes.html|archive-date=2017-06-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4.3.4修補了數個安全漏洞<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mashable.com/2011/07/15/ios-4-3-4-update/|title=Apple iOS 4.3.4 Update Available, Prevents Hacking & Jailbreaking|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2011-07-15|last=White|first=Charlie|website=[[Mashable|Mashable]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312174403/http://mashable.com/2011/07/15/ios-4-3-4-update/|archive-date=2017-03-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。iOS 4的最终版本<ref name=":12" /><ref name=":13" />——iOS 4.3.5则於2011年7月25日發布。此更新修正了[[憑證|憑證]]驗證的安全性問題<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://support.apple.com/kb/dl1431?locale=zh_TW|title=iOS 4.3.5 軟體更新|accessdate=2018-07-24|work=support.apple.com|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725102112/https://support.apple.com/kb/dl1431?locale=zh_TW|archive-date=2018-07-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1161328/ios435.html|title=Apple releases iOS 4.3.5 to fix certificate validation|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2011-07-25|last=Friedman|first=Lex|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510170138/http://www.macworld.com/article/1161328/ios435.html|archive-date=2017-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 系統新增功能 ==
在iOS 4中，由於資料夾功能的引入，主畫面能容納的最大程式數量從180個大幅提升至2160個<ref name=":14">{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100522132112/http://www.apple.com/tw/iphone/preview-iphone-os/|title=Apple - iPhone - iPhone OS 4 預覽|accessdate=2018-07-25|date=2010-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725102112/https://web.archive.org/web/20100522132112/http://www.apple.com/tw/iphone/preview-iphone-os/|archive-date=2018-07-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":15">{{Cite news|url=https://www.imore.com/ios-4-review|title=iOS 4 review|newspaper=iMore|accessdate=2018-07-25|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615111736/https://www.imore.com/ios-4-review|archive-date=2018-06-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不過在iOS 4中，一個資料夹最多只能放置12个应用程序<ref name=":17">{{Cite news|url=https://www.cultofmac.com/47653/review-ios-4-is-a-welcome-evolution-to-the-best-smartphone-platform/|title=Review: iOS 4 is a Welcome Evolution to the Best Smartphone Platform {{!}} Cult of Mac|date=2010-06-22|newspaper=Cult of Mac|accessdate=2018-07-25|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807034939/https://www.cultofmac.com/47653/review-ios-4-is-a-welcome-evolution-to-the-best-smartphone-platform/|archive-date=2017-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據容納的程式種類不同，資料夾的名稱也會隨之變化，當然也可以手動更改<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1152168/ios4folders.html|title=Hands on with iOS 4 folders|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-06-21|last=Frakes|first=Dan|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703204429/http://www.macworld.com/article/1152168/ios4folders.html|archive-date=2017-07-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外，還新增了自行更換主畫面[[桌布|桌布]]的功能，不過[[iPhone_3G|iPhone 3G]]及[[IPod_touch#第二代|第二代iPod touch]]則因為硬體效能問題而被排除在外<ref name=":17" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2010/06/22/steve-jobs-on-lack-of-custom-wallpapers-in-ios-4-for-iphone-3g/|title=Steve Jobs on Lack of Custom Wallpapers in iOS 4 for iPhone 3G|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-06-22|last=Slivka|first=Eric|website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801125229/https://www.macrumors.com/2010/06/22/steve-jobs-on-lack-of-custom-wallpapers-in-ios-4-for-iphone-3g/|archive-date=2017-08-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在iOS 4中，可以同时运行多个应用程序并隨時迅速切换，以讓部分应用程序在背景中運作，同時保有效能與電池續航力<ref name=":14" />。由於iOS 4的多工處理功能尚不完善，因此只有[[全球定位系统|定位]]、[[网络电话交换机|網路電話]]及[[媒体播放器|音樂播放]]等類型的應用程式能支援多工處理<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":17" /><ref name="What you need to know">{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1152167/ios4_need_to_know.html|title=iOS 4: What you need to know|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-06-21|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510170129/http://www.macworld.com/article/1152167/ios4_need_to_know.html|archive-date=2017-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/199528/Multitasking_With_iOS_4_is_Horrible_Apple_Blew_It.html|title=Multitasking With iOS 4 is Horrible: Apple Blew It|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-06-22|last=Newman|first=Jared|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[PC_World|PC World]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130629185931/http://www.pcworld.com/article/199528/Multitasking_With_iOS_4_is_Horrible_Apple_Blew_It.html|archive-date=2013-06-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同時，iOS 4引進了「快速切換」技術，能在使用者切換程式時保持其他背景程式運行<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":14" /><ref name=":15" />。

[[拼寫檢查|拼寫檢查]]最初於iPad版本的iPhone OS 3.2中出現<ref name=":15" />，而在iOS 4中引入所有裝置中。在輸入文字時，若出現拼字或文法錯誤，錯誤的地方會以紅底線標記，並提示正確的拼字或文法<ref name=":15" />。相机方面，在iOS 4中，可以最大五倍变焦倍率拍攝相片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/199431/apple_ios4_10_best_features.html#slide10|title=Apple iOS 4: 10 Best Features|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-06-21|last=Ionescu|first=Daniel|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[PC_World|PC World]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510211624/http://www.pcworld.com/article/199431/apple_ios4_10_best_features.html#slide10|archive-date=2017-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，在iOS 4.2中，首次為[[iPhone_4|iPhone 4]]加入了[[高動態範圍成像|HDR]]拍攝功能<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":15" />。

此外，iOS 4还有一大亮点，就是改进了最初於[[iPhone_OS_3|iPhone OS 3]]中出現的[[Spotlight_(應用程式)|Spotlight]]功能。在iOS 4中，Spotlight加入了[[Google搜索|Google搜尋]]及[[维基百科|維基百科]]的快捷搜尋選項，點選後會直接打開Safari應用程式顯示結果<ref name=":15" /><ref name="What you need to know" />。

== 應用程式新增功能 ==
在iOS 4中，可以在整合的收件箱内查看包含[[Gmail|Gmail]]、[[Yahoo!_Mail|Yahoo! Mail]]及[[Windows_Live_Hotmail|Hotmail]]等所有已登入郵件帐户中的邮件<ref name=":14" />，透過搜尋邮件標題及內文尋找郵件，還可以使用第三方应用程序開啟附件<ref name=":15" /><ref name=":17" />。iOS 4還加入了對[[MobileMe|MobileMe]]及[[Microsoft_Exchange_Server|Microsoft Exchange]]郵件帳戶的支援<ref name="What you need to know" />。

在iOS 4.1中，首次引入社群服務[[Game_Center|Game Center]]<ref name="appleDEV2" />。在Game Center中，用戶可透過在遊戲中獲得成就，在排行榜上競爭，並與其他來自世界各地的用戶交談<ref name="Game Center">{{cite web|url=https://www.apple.com/game-center/|title=Game Center|accessdate=2011-05-01|publisher=Apple Inc.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101223055005/https://www.apple.com/game-center|archive-date=2010-12-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1153821/software-games/ios-gamecenter.html|title=iOS 4.1's Game Center to hit iPhone next week|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-09-01|last=Holt|first=Chris|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180115215752/https://www.macworld.com/article/1153821/software-games/ios-gamecenter.html|archive-date=2018-01-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Game Center2">{{cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2010/09/08/download-ios-4-1-now-get-game-center-on-your-compatible-iprodu/|title=Download iOS 4.1 now, get Game Center (on your compatible iProduct)|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-09-08|last=Grant|first=Christopher|publisher=[[AOL|AOL]]|website=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180510185658/https://www.engadget.com/2010/09/08/download-ios-4-1-now-get-game-center-on-your-compatible-iprodu/|archive-date=2018-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此功能與iPhone 3G不相容<ref name="Game Center2" />。[[File:1st-Gen-iPad-WiFi-iBooks.jpg|缩略图]]
[[FaceTime|FaceTime]]是苹果推出的一种[[視訊電話|视频通话]]应用软件，使用该公司自定义的通信协议，於iOS 4首次推出<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cultofmac.com/488032/today-apple-history-ios-4-facetime-multitasking/|title=Today in Apple history: iOS 4 brings multitasking and FaceTime|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2017-06-21|last=Dormehl|first=Luke|website=Cult of Mac|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170622130759/https://www.cultofmac.com/488032/today-apple-history-ios-4-facetime-multitasking/|archive-date=2017-06-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="FaceTime Communications">{{cite web|url=http://facetime.com/LearnMore.aspx|title=Our name –FaceTime|accessdate=2010-06-07|author=FaceTime Communications|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100609083307/http://www.facetime.com/LearnMore.aspx|archivedate=2010-06-09|quote=Apple has announced that it will use 'FaceTime' as the trademark for its new video calling application.  Our agreement with Apple to transfer the FaceTime trademark to them comes as we are rebranding our company to better reflect our capabilities. We will be announcing a new name in the coming months.|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

在iOS 4中，於「搜尋引擎」選項內新增了[[Bing|Bing]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://searchengineland.com/bing-comes-to-the-iphone-43753|title=Bing Goes The iPhone|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-06-07|last=Sterling|first=Greg|website=[[Search_Engine_Land|Search Engine Land]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729085702/http://searchengineland.com/bing-comes-to-the-iphone-43753|archive-date=2017-07-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>；自iOS 4.2開始，可以在網頁內搜尋特定單字或句子<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imore.com/ios-42-features-find-text-safari-web-page|title=iOS 4.2 features: Find text on Safari web page|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-09-16|last=Ritchie|first=Rene|website=iMore|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312124653/http://www.imore.com/ios-42-features-find-text-safari-web-page|archive-date=2017-03-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

[[iBooks|iBooks]]最初於iPad推出，並於iOS 4中加入了對iPhone及iPod touch的支援<ref name=":15" /><ref name=":18">{{cite web|url=https://www.cultofmac.com/47634/ios-4-ibooks-for-iphone-now-available-for-download/|title=iOS 4, iBooks for iPhone Now Available For Download|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-06-21|last=Brownlee|first=John|website=Cult of Mac|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180510184500/https://www.cultofmac.com/47634/ios-4-ibooks-for-iphone-now-available-for-download/|archive-date=2018-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過iBooks不是內建軟體，而是作為一款[[App_Store_(iOS)|App Store]]應用程式推出<ref name=":18" /><ref name=":19">{{Cite news|url=https://www.kocpc.com.tw/archives/787|title=[轉貼]iOS4的 iBooks介面介紹 - 電腦王阿達|date=2010-06-24|newspaper=電腦王阿達|accessdate=2018-07-25|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725102112/https://www.kocpc.com.tw/archives/787|archive-date=2018-07-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在iOS 4更新中，iBooks加入了[[書籤|書籤]]及筆記功能，並與Apple ID同步<ref name=":15" /><ref name=":19" />。另外，iBooks新增了對[[可移植文档格式|PDF]]文件的支援，PDF文件將放置於第二個書架中<ref name=":15" /><ref name=":19" />。

== 問題 ==
{{參見|iPhone 4#iPhone 4訊號減弱或斷訊的情況(天線門事件)|l1=天線門事件}}
iOS 4推出後，部分iPhone 3G使用者回報，在升級至iOS 4後，裝置效能下降、電池壽命縮減，蘋果自2010年7月開始檢視問題所在<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-to-investigate-ios-4-problems-on-iphone-3g/|title=Apple to investigate iOS 4 problems on iPhone 3G|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-07-28|last=Ogg|first=Erica|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022115202/https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-to-investigate-ios-4-problems-on-iphone-3g/|archive-date=2016-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年11月，蘋果由於此問題遭到不滿的用戶控訴。該名用戶者宣稱蘋果違反了《{{le|加州消費者保護方案|California Consumer Privacy Act}}》，進行不當商業宣傳，明知軟體更新會造成舊型裝置效能下降，仍宣稱無影響<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/slow-iphone-3g-ios-update-could-be-on-the-way/|title=Slow iPhone 3G? iOS update could be on the way|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-08-20|last=Ogg|first=Erica|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180510185916/https://www.cnet.com/news/slow-iphone-3g-ios-update-could-be-on-the-way/|archive-date=2018-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-sued-for-ios-4-problems-on-iphone-3g-3gs/|title=Apple sued for iOS 4 problems on iPhone 3G, 3GS|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-11-04|last=Ogg|first=Erica|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180510185101/https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-sued-for-ios-4-problems-on-iphone-3g-3gs/|archive-date=2018-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 蘋果隨後在iOS 4.1更新中解決了問題<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":21" />。

此外，部分iPhone 4使用者還回報了[[天线|天線]]收訊不良的問題<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wired.com/2010/07/iphone-4-anandtech|title=Tests confirm iPhone 4's antenna flaws (Updated)|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-07-02|last=Chen|first=Brian X.|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|website=[[Wired_(website)|Wired]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510195154/https://www.wired.com/2010/07/iphone-4-anandtech/|archive-date=2017-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.mcbub.com/index.php/electronics/apple-accessories-geeky-iphone-4-cases-weekly-round-up-919-924/|title=Geeky iPhone 4 Cases Weekly Round Up|accessdate=2014-03-18|date=|publisher=Blog.mcbub.com|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120713011424/http://blog.mcbub.com/index.php/electronics/apple-accessories-geeky-iphone-4-cases-weekly-round-up-919-924/|archivedate=2012-07-13|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。 蘋果企圖透過iOS 4.0.1更新解決此問題<ref name=":20" />，然而成效不彰<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/201297/apples_iphone_4_antenna_gate_timeline.html|title=Apple's iPhone 4 Antennagate Timeline|accessdate=2017-07-15|date=2010-07-17|last=Ionescu|first=Daniel|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[PC_World|PC World]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170715142545/http://www.pcworld.com/article/201297/apples_iphone_4_antenna_gate_timeline.html|archive-date=2017-07-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

